### Test Query Optimizer Analyze Endpoint - Fixed ConnectionId Type
POST https://localhost:7189/api/query-optimizer/analyze
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM Users WHERE Id = 1",
  "connectionId": "your-connection-guid-here",
  "includeExecutionPlan": false
}

### Test Query Optimizer Analyze With Plan Endpoint
POST https://localhost:7189/api/query-optimizer/analyze-with-plan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "sql": "SELECT * FROM Users WHERE Id = 1",
  "connectionId": "your-connection-guid-here"
}
